Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:06.99,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:09.55,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In this kingdom where magic is everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:12.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,there is one boy who can't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:15.25,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:18.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,With guts and hard work, \Nhe made it into the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:21.75,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and he never gave up, \Ndespite how much he got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:24.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He continues to diligently aim for the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:27.81,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are a peasant,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:29.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,or even if you're poor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:32.38,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone in this world can still shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:34.80,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He's working hard to prove that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:37.78,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and to become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:47.67,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of the Black Bulls and I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:49.23,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,are training so that we can
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:52.19,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,go up against the Spade Kingdom and that devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:01:01.04,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But at this rate... we don't stand \Na chance against their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:05.46,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Rouge...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:16.36,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Now's not the time to \Nworry about how I get things done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.53,0:01:24.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,There ain't no shops open this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:27.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:30.73,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:37.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I just wandered down here, and this \Nbottle invited me to have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:46.25,main,yami,0000,0000,0000,,What? You mad I'm drinking \Nfrom your secret stash?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:48.80,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No, have as much as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:50.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're not drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:52.25,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:57.08,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to enjoy a drink with you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:58.76,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:01.76,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to have to ask for a rain check.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:03.76,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.51,0:02:06.77,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to have one next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:09.95,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:12.35,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:35.73,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(210,1871)\t(210,2419,\fscx120\fscy120)}A Witch's Homecoming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:47.24,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(739,1)}Queen of Witches
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:52.64,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to ask a favor of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:59.42,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to tell me how I can \Nstrengthen my friends and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.28,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fighting the Spade Kingdom soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:07.43,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The Witches' Forest will be in danger, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.67,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,I am fully aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:15.31,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Not only of your actions, but also of \Nthe threat heading toward our forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:20.07,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,It is unfathomable that \NI would not be aware of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.76,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Then you understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:26.20,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,They possess mana far greater \Nthan that of any normal mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:30.58,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have to fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:36.53,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,And my friends only know how to \Nfight by pushing themselves too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:43.59,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle that we haven't \Nlost anyone yet because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.73,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:53.62,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,You already have the power to change fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:55.19,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.19,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Rouge is not all-powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:03.69,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose my mana, Rouge also \Nloses her power to change fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:07.55,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Please... teach me some of the ancient magic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.16,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,that lies within the Witches' Forest,\N which only you know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:15.41,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I need your powers in order to fight them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:20.30,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you could actually use my magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:22.67,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,I fail to see the point in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:24.47,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Then just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:27.80,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me the ancient magic \Nthat lies in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.37,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:33.92,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:38.31,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I escaped this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:43.03,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,so I know I'm out of line \Nto even ask for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.28,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:49.87,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't gain anything here,\N my friends will...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:55.46,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm not saying there \Nisn't a way to give you power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:06:01.38,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:09.39,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,So you must be, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:15.41,sign_8858_69_Samantha_Kravitz,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(481,536)}Samantha Kravitz
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:15.41,sign_8858_70_Elvira_Aguirre,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(481,536)}Elvira Aguirre
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.98,top,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Samantha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:15.41,top,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you, Miss Vanessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:19.85,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Samantha, and you're... Elvira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.46,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen of Witches told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:25.12,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only doing this because \Nthe Queen ordered me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:28.07,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,But you're not my superior, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:31.82,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know that. So it'd be \Ngreat if you could lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:42.25,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.89,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,We have security golems \Nplaced outside the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:51.05,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,to notify us if the \NSpade Kingdom attacks, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:04.07,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Security golems will react to any threat,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:06.40,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,but they can't tell humans \Nfrom magical beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:08.37,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,They'd never stop otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:13.45,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,so the Queen has set them to\Nstop shooting after three shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:17.03,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, when the \NSpade Kingdom actually attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:20.12,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,they won't be much help as an early defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.56,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,And you were told to make them useful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:26.79,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen of Witches herself \Ngave you special treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.63,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm sure that'd be an easy task for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.75,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:33.03,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:34.05,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.24,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,There are magical beasts staring at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.59,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot attack spells at them!\NAny ones you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.70,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,They should flee after one hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.60,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:08:00.11,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, didn't you defeat the last \Nenemy that invaded this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:12.89,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,Or what? Are you useless without the \Nhelp of men from the outside world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.60,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,Elvira, that's not very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:16.88,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:19.40,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,Well, back then, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:20.72,flashback,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Team Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.90,flashback,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare underestimate us witches!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:34.50,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't need to bring that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:42.41,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I never asked what kind of magic \Nyou two possess. Could you show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:43.57,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:51.87,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Sound magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:54.87,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,This is all I can do. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:57.29,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for showing me. And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.35,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Magic that projects illusions?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.49,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:08.36,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. You've got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:13.36,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's my fault for not \Nconfirming your powers first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.28,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I really can't do this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:22.46,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm absolutely useless. \NI'm just going to hold you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:26.23,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,You should just give up this job already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.67,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,We're both failures, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:34.51,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The way Samantha panics is just like Grey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.97,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,And Elvira being so proud \Nreminds me of Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:43.60,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What's really so different \Nbetween them and these girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.74,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wrap things up for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:51.53,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to go. I'll think\N of something by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:52.62,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:54.88,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,Not like anything's going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:00.61,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Those two won't be enough help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:06.11,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,When the time for war comes,\NI will need everyone out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:09.24,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,So you want me to train them \Nuntil they'll be useful in battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:12.00,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But who knows how long that'll take?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:16.01,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now. So that was your plan all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.09,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:23.72,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to get me to give up by \Ngiving me a task that's impossible to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:28.23,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you use your magic for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:34.31,main,Witch A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:38.75,main,Witch B,0000,0000,0000,,About how the Queen's making her \Ndeal with those two failures, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:42.45,main,Witch C,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's not happening. \NI mean, it's Samantha and Elvira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.92,main,Wtich A,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen of Witches can be so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:51.22,main,Witch B,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how special Vanessa might be, \Nthere are things even she can't pull off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:52.46,main,Witch C,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.96,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:58.22,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the witches here never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:03.45,flashback,Witch 1,0000,0000,0000,,That cake shop ended up closing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.72,flashback,Witch 2,0000,0000,0000,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:08.45,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The witches in this forest love to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:12.71,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never gotten to \Njoin their conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:14.98,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That probably goes for those two, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:20.07,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut you a deal! Act now, \Nand it'll only be 20,000 yuls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.13,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Are you buying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:22.39,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Why, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:24.88,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:30.51,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey. It's been a while. How've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:32.29,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Domina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:44.58,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's why you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:46.56,top,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:50.62,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(482,536)}Dominante Code
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:51.12,top,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know that hubby of \Nmine can't work a normal job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:52.85,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,He's a wanted man, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:56.08,top,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,He has nothing better to do,\N so he's been farming,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:58.32,sign_17116_158_Fanzel_Kruger,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(510,478)\blur3}Fanzell Kruger
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:58.32,sign_17116_159_Mariella,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(510,478)\blur3}Mariella
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:58.35,top,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,but that's not enough to put food on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:03.54,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I have to peddle these magic items.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:05.49,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.87,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you got permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:12.37,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, considering I escaped \Nthis place, just like you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:16.36,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing the Queen thinks \Nit might benefit her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:20.55,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}are{\i0} a pretty good magic item saleswoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.78,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but sounds like you're having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:26.89,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure. I'm at a loss right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:30.77,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have the perfect magic item for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:35.43,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magic washboard that gets any \Nstain out, depending on the user's mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:38.27,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, so I'll cut \Nthe price down to 8,000 yuls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:41.19,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to use \Nthis against magical beasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.10,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:44.53,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna buy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.89,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:49.55,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I buy something that I'm \Nnot even sure will be of any use?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:52.79,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, it's always about how you use things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:58.84,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen of Witches manages to \Nkeep all the witches here in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.41,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:03.79,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:04.59,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:12.85,flashbackitalics,Queen of Witches,0000,0000,0000,,What do you use your magic for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:20.81,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,All right. The three of us are going to get
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.98,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,those magical beasts away from the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.26,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:27.98,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:31.08,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. We can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.56,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're the only ones who can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:39.42,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,You seem pretty confident for \Nsome reason. Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:41.67,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I am. Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:46.30,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Witches' Forest. \NThis is the magical beasts' territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:50.90,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Smaller magical beasts gather \Naround here to eat nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:55.15,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,And bigger magical beasts \Nfeed on those smaller ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.50,main,Vanssa,0000,0000,0000,,And right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.59,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of trees \Nthat are loaded with nuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:02.34,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,so a lot of small magical beasts gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.86,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a number of bigger magical beasts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:06.24,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,You saw them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.82,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I stayed up all night investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.04,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You finally looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:13.48,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,S-So?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.73,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:21.01,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lead the larger magical beasts that \Ncome near the Witches' Forest this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.96,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Then they won't come here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:26.20,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,How is that simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:29.13,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think we can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.57,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:32.68,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We can. It's not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:38.48,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I was just like you two. I'd given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:39.85,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.87,main,Little witch A,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:46.07,main,Little witch B,0000,0000,0000,,Dollies?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.63,main,Little witch C,0000,0000,0000,,They're so little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:52.88,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Think back... to the first time \Nyou were able to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:57.78,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's thought about what they \Nwanted to use their magic for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:14:59.50,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,As for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:01.83,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to make everyone smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:05.00,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That was the one thing I couldn't give up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:09.00,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I don't want to see anyone cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:13.75,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be even more wonderful \Nif the dolls had color?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:14.77,main,Little wtich A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:18.89,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.07,main,Little witches,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:25.64,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,And believe it or not, these dolls talk, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:26.65,main,Little witches,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.28,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:34.52,main,Doll A,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to this. I got hit on \Nin town again yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:35.80,main,Doll B,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:39.12,main,Doll C,0000,0000,0000,,But the only ones who ever talk to \Nyou are old guys and little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:44.79,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Any type of magic can be used for\Nall kinds of things, depending on
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:46.17,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,how you use and combine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:52.32,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that made those kids smile \Nwas none other than our magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:55.68,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:16.45,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.63,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Good, you two. Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:40.85,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Elvira!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.56,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:50.32,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,We've been running a while... \NAre we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.34,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The markers I left last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:55.61,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.32,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.12,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:04.62,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:15.09,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:19.18,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No! Those are actual little magical beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:21.59,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,But we came this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:23.18,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do? Run?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.69,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:34.57,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Elvira! I need you to make this \Nas terrifying as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.57,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:44.82,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Samantha! Make it roar! \NMake it sound really, really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:46.46,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:02.22,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Our plan worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:05.44,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,We actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.98,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,...did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.48,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:14.39,main,Witch A,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:16.49,main,Witch B,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:17.77,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:19.49,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.87,main,Witch C,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen showed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:29.50,main,Samantha,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:30.99,main,Elvira,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:35.11,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You two found something you \Ndidn't want to give up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:38.14,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you never forget what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:41.67,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:46.46,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,All of my dummies are absolutely \Nterrible at giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:54.15,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:19:00.16,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to learn some powerful spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.91,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,but never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:02.91,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:08.75,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to train myself \Nand gradually raise my mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:13.17,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'll continue thinking about \Nthe best way to use my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.34,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.46,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I can do, and that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:19.81,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,So you were able to tug the \Nthreads of people's emotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:23.69,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Those threads were always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:27.62,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to continue to \Nuse my magic so that all my
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.98,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,friends in the Black Bulls \Ncan always keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:35.67,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,As you said, I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:39.53,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't Rouge's magic that could change fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.78,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the day I left this forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.28,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Choose for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:51.79,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me the opportunity, but he's \Nnot the one who changed my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:55.99,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who chose my path, \Nand I'm the one who changed my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:20:01.06,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to continue to change \Nthe worst fate that may befall us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:06.77,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pull together the \Nthreads that will connect to the fate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:08.39,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,that keeps everyone smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:13.66,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Then go. You have no reason to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:20.42,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:23.90,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you going home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:26.32,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I wanted to thank you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:28.87,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,"Too"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:30.53,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:33.66,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to thank me, buy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:37.88,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,This is a magic item that \Nyou put in the bath, and then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.37,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,bubbles flow out of these holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:41.10,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,It's great for relaxation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:45.77,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's on sale for the \Nspecial low price of 12,000 yuls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:46.93,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:47.75,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:51.10,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've earned plenty \Nwithout me having to buy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:55.82,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. It's great that \NI can run my business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:58.05,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to the Queen of Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:02.04,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Despite what she says, she still looks after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:03.11,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:06.93,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Fanzell and Mariella hi for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:09.13,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Asta and the others hi for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:14.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:17.96,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:20.09,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:22.21,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:25.72,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So, you learn any new spells?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:27.95,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No, not a single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:29.74,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:31.47,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:36.10,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be a lot left, \Nconsidering your usual pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:40.11,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted to have a drink \Nwith me, so I saved some for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:41.71,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:45.54,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'll have to take a rain check again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:46.95,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:51.87,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to lay off for a while\N so I can train properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:21:54.15,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:57.00,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm heading to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:21:59.76,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:01.50,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:04.01,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:07.08,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.15,0:23:41.71,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Queen of Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:45.48,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I know what path I need to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:50.36,main,Some,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 140:\N "A Favor for Julius."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 140\N\N{\fs18} A Favor for Julius
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:53.06,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is that Sally?!
